---
title: Beyond Meat®, Sweet Pepper and Black Bean Taquitos with Monterey Jack Cheese and Fresh Salad
description: Nutritious and delicious black beans take centre stage in this fun veggie recipe. Cooked with Beyond Meat®, sweet onions, peppers and zesty chipotle sauce, everything is then wrapped and baked with stretchy Monterey Jack cheese for ultimate cheese pull satisfaction!
